cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Meissa, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Meissa: Multi-modal Medical Agentic Intelligence"
abstract: >
  Meissa is a lightweight 4B-parameter medical multi-modal LLM that brings
  full agentic capability offline. It unifies four heterogeneous medical
  agent environments (Continuous Tool Calling, Interleaved Thinking with
  Images, Multi-Agent Collaboration, and Multi-turn Clinical Simulation)
  through unified trajectory modeling, three-tier stratified supervision,
  and prospective-retrospective trajectory supervision.
